snippet.textDisplay:
I love y'all so much! Y'all have inspired me to do many things and I love joining y'all with my friends and try not to laugh at the things that y'all do!!! Here are some ideas for another video:

1. Blind Folded- You should blind fold the person that is trying to make the person in the seat laugh and they have to do there act blindfolded.

2. Pick the Animal- The Person in the seat can pick any animal that they want the person that is about to make them laugh be. And they the person in the seat tells them right before they go on which makes it funnier and a little bit more challenging.

3. Courtney Courtney ( say it with a British accent )- for this one Courtney gets to pick what accent you have before you preform. If you fail to do the accents Courtney is able to choose someone that isn't her to put ice either down your shirt or in your pants. if you say no to that then you are out.

4. Blue Hair don't Care- Usual rules that you always have but if you don't make the person in the chair laugh they have to get there hair sprayed what ever color the person in the chair wants them to do.

5. Glasses with Curls- for this one you have to wear a pair of drunk glasses and try to do an act in them. It will be a lot easier than usual because you would just be falling over an doing random stuff the whole time. And you can barely see so that is what makes it cool. ( you might want to put up a barrier between the stage and the camera people so the nothing gets broken or stepped on when someone has the glasses on. )

6. Blonde and Buff Baby- For this one you have to use at least two other people for your skit THAT ARE BEHIND THE CAMERAS but they don't have a clue whats going on IF they catch on and follow along with the process BUT if they don't the person who picked them both has to put on a blonde wig and do 10 much ups while people are stacking stuff on top of there back. ( NO GIRL PUSH UPS )

I have more ideas but these are just the best ones.

Have fun!!!
